</div></section><p>We created visualization to compare the distribution of the actual provider interaction time and predicted provider interaction time in <strong><a href="#f1-2977274" class="usa-link">Figure 1</a></strong>. In addition, the difference of the provider interaction time between predicted value and actual value was shown in <strong><a href="#f2-2977274" class="usa-link">Figure 2</a></strong>.</p>
<figure class="fig xbox font-sm" id="f1-2977274"><h4 class="obj_head">Figure 1:</h4>
